One percent a day = 3800 percent a year.</p>
</blockquote>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p><strong>Review and record</strong> what went well and whatÂ didnâ€™t.</p>

    <p>Review and record what went well and whatÂ didnâ€™t. . Evaluate what worked and what didnâ€™t.Â Only 15 minutes of composed reflection toward the dayâ€™s end expanded execution by 23% for one gathering of workers.</p>
