<blockquote>
  <p>When I was learning poker, my friends and I would compare notes on every difficult hand we played during an evening. When I was learning investing, Iâ€™d talk to friends in every area of investing (day trading, arbitrage, value investing, special situations, quantitative, etc etc) and weâ€™d share notes and quickly learn through the experiences of each other.
