<ul>
  <li>
    <p><strong>Do.</strong></p>

    <p>If itâ€™s possible to do it, do it â€“ donâ€™t just think it. If youâ€™re sure you know what the result will be, do it anyway. The human brain plugs more easily into the concrete than the abstract.Â </p>

